The program can be launched by using the 'hapiest.sh' script. If you cannot launch the script by
double clicking it, you will have to run it in a terminal. Open a terminal and cd into the directory 
that contains 'hapiest.sh' and simply invoke:

./hapiest.sh

If you encounter trouble, please open in issue on the Github page: 
https://github.com/hitranonline/hapiest/issues
